This is the ansible certservice installer

prerequisites
-------------

On your build host:

1) Ansible

   see: http://docs.ansible.com/
   via git:  git clone https://github.com/ansible/ansible.git



On the target:

1) Ansible 'as-root' controller

   /data/local/bin/ansible_command

   see: (ansibletools)/host-tools


2) Directories to be chown to 'iamcert.iam-dev'

   /etc/daemons/tomcat
   /data/webapps
   /data/conf/apache.conf.d/
   /logs/cs/
   /www/ (?)
   /data/local/cs
  
3) configure tomcat to run as user=iamcert

---------------------

Install
--------

   
1) Make the package.  In base product directory:  ( with a java 1.8 compiler )

   $ mvn clean package

2) To install the service: 
   ( host_type = tools_dev | tools_eval | tools_prod )
  
   $ ./install.sh <host_type>

3) To install the utilities:

   $ ./install.sh -p install-util.yml <host_type>
